\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Yeah, that makes a lot of sense \'97 and it's actually a smart expansion of the core concept.\
Right now the mental model is 
\f2\b setlist-to-clip
\f0\b0  (song 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  footage). But a live event experience is way more than the performance itself. The journey 
\f4\i is
\f0\i0  the content:\
