\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 The Core Insight\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Instagram and TikTok are 
\f2\b broadcast platforms
\f0\b0  \'97 you post 
\f4\i to your followers
\f0\i0 . Showside is an 
\f2\b archive platform
\f0\b0  \'97 you post 
\f4\i to the show
\f0\i0 .\
Those aren't competing motivations. They're sequential. Post the highlight to TikTok for clout, then upload the full 3-minute clip to Showside because it belongs there permanently. Same person, same night, different jobs.\
The framing that unlocks this: 
\f2\b Showside is where the show lives forever. TikTok is where you go viral today.
\f0\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \strokec5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 What You're Actually Competing With\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 You're not really competing with TikTok for attention. You're competing with 
\f2\b doing nothing
\f0\b0  \'97 the 47 clips sitting in someone's camera roll that never got posted anywhere because they weren't "good enough" for Instagram. That's your actual addressable content pool. It's enormous.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \strokec5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 What Works In Your Favor\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 No performance anxiety.
\f0\b0  On Instagram every post is a referendum on your personal brand. On Showside nobody cares if your clip is shaky \'97 it's fan footage, that's the point. Lower bar = more uploads.\

\f2\b The event as context.
\f0\b0  When someone uploads to Showside they're contributing to 
\f4\i the show's record
\f0\i0  not their personal feed. That's a different and lower-pressure motivation.\

\f2\b The QR code at the venue.
\f0\b0  You already have this in the schema. A QR code at the show that says 
\f4\i "Upload your footage here"
\f0\i0  catches people in the moment before they even think about Instagram.\

\f2\b Cross-posting is fine.
\f0\b0  You don't need exclusivity. If someone uploads to both TikTok and Showside, you win. You got the content. Their TikTok post might even drive viewers to Showside.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \strokec5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

