\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 If even one artist or team 
\f2\b officially acknowledges Showside
\f0\b0  \'97 a tweet, a story, a mention \'97 the upload behavior follows immediately. Fan communities are extremely responsive to signals from the artist. That's probably the single highest-leverage distribution move in V1.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
