\f0  the page looks incredible 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  a bigger artist's team sees it 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  repeat.\
You don't need Taylor Swift in month one. You need one artist with a passionate enough fanbase to seed the content, and the flywheel starts.\
