\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 Content Quality Incentives\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Full song bonus
\f0\b0  Video over 2.5 minutes gets a "Full Song" badge on the card and surfaces higher in the setlist view. You mentioned this \'97 it's smart because it directly improves the virtual attendance experience.\

\f2\b First upload bonus
\f0\b0  First person to upload from a specific show gets a "First There" badge permanently on that media. Early upload behavior is incredibly valuable \'97 you want footage up before the buzz dies.\

\f2\b Coverage completeness
\f0\b0  If uploads collectively cover every song in a setlist, the event page gets a 
\f2\b "Full Show Captured"
\f0\b0  banner. This creates collaborative pressure \'97 fans see which songs are missing and go hunting in their camera roll.\

\f2\b Rarity badge
\f0\b0  If only 1-2 people filmed a specific moment \'97 a surprise guest, a rarely played deep cut \'97 that clip gets a 
\f2\b "Rare Moment"
\f0\b0  badge. Scarcity = perceived value.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \strokec5 \
