\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 Social / Competitive Mechanics\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Show leaderboard
\f0\b0  Each event page has a top contributors list \'97 "Most uploaded from this show." Small but visible. Creates friendly competition among fans who attended the same night.\

\f2\b Artist leaderboard
\f0\b0  Across all shows for an artist \'97 who has contributed the most to this artist's archive. This is the one superfans will actually care about deeply.\

\f2\b Streak system
\f0\b0  Uploaded from 3 shows in a row? You're on a streak. Displayed on profile. Encourages repeat behavior across the touring season.\

\f2\b City champion
\f0\b0  Top uploader from each city gets a subtle geo badge. "Chicago's top contributor" means something to a local fan community.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \strokec5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 Discovery / Curation Incentives\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Community picks
\f0\b0  Top liked clip of each show gets automatically featured in the hero position on the event page. The uploader gets notified \'97 
\f4\i "Your clip was voted the best moment from last night's show."
\f0\i0  That notification is incredibly motivating.\

\f2\b Setlist MVP
\f0\b0  Most liked clip for each song on the setlist gets a small crown. Visible to everyone browsing that song's clips. Creates competition per song not just per show.\

\f2\b Editor's picks
\f0\b0  Manual curation by Showside (or eventually community moderators) \'97 a human selects the best clip of the week across all shows. Featured on the homepage. The uploader gets a permanent "Editor's Pick" badge on that clip.\
