\f0\fs24 \cf6 \strokec6 Build the complete upload flow UI. This is the most important UX in the \
app \'97 target under 60 seconds from opening page to upload complete on mobile.\
\
The flow has 4 steps rendered as a single-page progressive UI (no full \
page navigations between steps):\
\
STEP 1 \'97 Event Picker\
- Search input: type artist or venue name\
- Calls existing /api/search endpoint\
- Results show: artist/team name 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  their upcoming/recent events listed below\
- User taps an event to select it\
- Selected event shown as a confirmation chip at top with X to change\
- "Can't find your event?" link 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  simple form to suggest it (just saves \
  to a suggestions table, no immediate action)\
\
STEP 2 \'97 File Select\
- Large tap target: "Add photos & videos"\
- Opens native file picker: accept="image/*,video/*" multiple\
- Selected files shown as thumbnail grid\
- Each thumbnail has an X to remove\
- File count and total size shown\
- Max 20 files, max 500MB total \'97 show friendly error if exceeded\
- "Add more" button to append files\
\
STEP 3 \'97 Optional Tagging (keep this very light)\
- Shown after file select, before upload starts\
- Single question: "Where were you?" with pill options:\
  Pit / Floor / Seated / VIP / Outside / Concourse\
- Optional \'97 "Skip" is prominent, not hidden\
- No song tagging in this step \'97 that's auto-classified later\
- This is the only manual input we ask for\
\
STEP 4 \'97 Upload + Success\
- Upload button starts all transfers simultaneously\
- Progress: overall progress bar + "X of Y files uploaded"\
- Each file uploads to its correct endpoint:\
  - Images 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  /api/photo-url (presigned R2) then PUT to R2\
  - Videos 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  /api/video-url (Mux direct upload URL) then PUT to Mux URL\
  - On each completion 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  POST /api/upload-complete\
- On full completion 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  Success screen:\
  "Your footage is now part of [Event Name]'s archive"\
  Show count of uploads\
  Soft account prompt: "Create an account to track your shows and get \
  notified when your clips get likes" \'97 dismissible\
  "View the show" button 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  navigates to event page\
  "Upload more" button 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  resets flow\
\
Technical notes:\
- All uploads are anonymous (no auth required) \'97 use existing session token\
- Use existing API routes exactly as built \'97 don't modify them\
- Show upload speed / estimated time remaining if possible\
- Handle errors per-file: failed files shown in red with retry button\
- Mobile-first: all tap targets minimum 44px, thumb-friendly layout\
- Accessible from: event page Upload tab, homepage CTA, direct URL /upload\
