\f2\b \cf0 \strokec2 Database Schema
\f0\b0 \
Six core tables: entities, events, media, users, likes, follows. Additional tables: attended_events, event_suggestions, media_views (Phase 6).\
DB triggers maintain all counters (upload_count, like_count, follower_count, show_count) in-transaction. Anon likes use partial unique index on (media_id, session_token) where user_id is null.\
Media status flow: uploading 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  active (photos on /complete, videos on Mux webhook).\
Key media columns: id, event_id, entity_id, uploader_id, upload_session, file_type, storage_url, mux_asset_id, mux_upload_id, mux_playback_id, thumbnail_url, duration_sec, song_tag, section_tag, is_full_song, status, view_count, like_count.\
Supabase project ID: iuxhlflulrpoppuwnrxg / Region: us-west-2\
